827776539.itemDescription:
An order for a Häkke Herja-D Pulse Rifle.

Foundry orders are delivered via the Gunsmith on Armsday, which occurs every Wednesday.

837448826.itemDescription: Defeat 3 opposing Guardians with precision shots.
837448826.displaySource: "If you're not aimin' at the soft parts, you're makin' it a lot harder on yourself. And on them." —Cayde-6.

891614685.itemDescription: Kill enemies in Level 41 Prison of Elders or Challenge of the Elders.
891614685.displaySource: "The strong survive. The weak are judged." —Variks

915115332.itemDescription:
An order for a Häkke Strongbow-D Shotgun.

Foundry orders are delivered via the Gunsmith on Armsday, which occurs every Wednesday.

937555249.itemDescription:
A brilliant spark of the Traveler's Light.

Can be consumed to apply experience to your equipped gear.
937555249.displaySource: Obtained from Weekly Heroics, Public Events and dismantling upgraded gear.

954129692.itemDescription:
Contains 1 Silver Dust, 1 Exotic Weapon Ornament, and up to 2 possible additional items.

This item is nonreturnable.

1129051958.itemDescription:
An order for an Omolon Kumakatok HC4 Hand Cannon.

Foundry orders are delivered via the Gunsmith on Armsday, which occurs every Wednesday.

1133804624.itemDescription:
An order for a SUROS DIS-43 Scout Rifle.

Foundry orders are delivered via the Gunsmith on Armsday, which occurs every Wednesday.

1157478132.itemDescription: Use Arc abilities to kill enemies in Level 41 Prison of Elders or Challenge of the Elders.
1157478132.displaySource: "Arc energy a very powerful weapon, yes? Bright, blinding… deadly." —Variks

1209869507.displaySource: "Our battle with the Hive may never end. But we can make them regret starting the fight." —Eris Morn

1209869517.displaySource: "The Darkness always finds new ways to destroy us. We must stand firm." —Ikora Rey

1275480033.itemDescription: "When one can wield the fire of stars, what use is flesh and bone?"

1311569433.itemDescription: Complete a match in any team playlist where you or a member of your Fireteam finishes with the highest score.
1311569433.displaySource: "Sometimes, an individual can eclipse the Fireteam. It's good. Makes the others see how it's done." —Lord Shaxx

1314964292.itemDescription: Complete Dreg encounters in the Archon's Forge.

The Devils seek to prove themselves in the Archon's Forge. They offer SIVA to appease their Priests, then fight for their lives to prove their worth.

Make an offering to incite Dregs in the Forge, then wipe them out.

The purity of the SIVA Offering impacts progress.

1395828771.displaySource: Defeat any Fallen in the Plaguelands to keep them from rallying.

1596883705.itemDescription: Revive 3 teammates in the Skirmish playlist.
1596883705.displaySource: "A Fireteam that supports itself can fight indefinitely, to our enemies' chagrin." —Lord Shaxx

1621282040.itemDescription:
An order for a Häkke Gaheris-D Hand Cannon.

Foundry orders are delivered via the Gunsmith on Armsday, which occurs every Wednesday.

1797491610.displaySource: Commonly found among the ruins on the Moon.

2601444956.itemDescription: Suros prototype. Use in the Crucible to gather data for the Suros research department.

Said to be used by the Nine to transform the properties of Exotic gear.
2633085824.displaySource: Obtained from Xûr, Agent of the Nine.

2670104629.itemDescription:
Equip this Weapon Ornament to change Hawkmoon's appearance.
Dismantle for 5 Silver Dust.

2759745988.itemDescription:
Defeat enemies in the Prison of Elders to gain notoriety with the House of Judgment.

Raise your standing to unlock better rewards.

2845071044.itemDescription: Use the Iron Battle Axe or powerful enemy weapons to decimate hostile threats.
2845071044.displaySource: Wield powerful weapons. Destroy your enemies.

2990972208.itemDescription: Consume to receive House of Judgment reputation.

3109888176.itemDescription: A volatile synthesis of energized matter and self-modifying energy constructs.
3109888176.displaySource: Obtained from Nightfall Strikes, the Prison of Elders and awarded for renowned performance in the Trials of Osiris.

3159615086.itemDescription: The currency of the City. A programmable matter used as a source of power before the Collapse. Glimmer is shared between all your characters.

3262574748.itemDescription: Defeat 2 opposing Guardians with a single Fist of Havoc activation.
3262574748.displaySource: "When a Striker turns her entire body into a projectile, no one is truly safe." —Commander Zavala

3763238211.displaySource: "Nightstalkers have many friends. It's the bow. Everyone loves the bow." —Cayde-6

3763238222.displaySource: "Guardians spoiled by Light, by Ghosts who spare them from death. Are you spoiled?" —Variks, the Loyal

3763238223.displaySource: "Hate to admit it, but sometimes a Guardian's Light can reach places her gun can't." —Banshee-44

3938709034.itemDescription:
"You are not welcome." —Unknown
"I beg to differ." —Shiro-4

4001686418.itemDescription: Win any Crucible match (except Mayhem matches)  with an individual score of at least 2500 points.
4001686418.displaySource: "Don't just aim to win. Aim to kick their teeth in." —Cayde-6

4085991207.itemDescription: Collect resource nodes, open chests and kill enemies on the Moon.
4085991207.displaySource: "The Moon is synonymous with the Hive. The Armory recommends at least one Solar weapon for any Guardian traveling there." —Roni 55-30

4153321881.itemDescription: Kill Champions in Level 41 Prison of Elders or Challenge of the Elders.
4153321881.displaySource: "Leaders must fall before armies can be defeated." —Variks

4174604995.itemDescription: In Skirmish, defeat opposing Guardians who have already been damaged by a teammate.
4174604995.displaySource: "The Walls hold because of a joint effort, not because of any one Guardian." —Commander Zavala

4268984314.itemDescription: Complete Servitor encounters in the Archon's Forge.
4268984314.displaySource:
A Fallen who makes an offering of SIVA to the Archon's Forge, and survives their trial, will be granted augmentation or enhancement through SIVA.

Make an offering to incite Servitors in the Forge. Destroy them all.

The purity of the SIVA Offering impacts progress.
